{
  "stem": "56.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I think my father knew, because at the station, before we got on the train, they gave each one of us a whole bread and a bottle of oil.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they said, you might be traveling a few days to your new destination, so this is gonna be the food for you.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A bottle of black oil and a bread-- pretty sized big bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So while we were on the train, we were-- as usual, we were very hungry, and we had this bread.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So everybody started to eat the bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody was eating, and my dad said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] eat as much as you want.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my-- not my sister, because she wasn't with us at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My cousin was with me, but that's a different story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she said, don't eat the whole bread, because you-- you were told we don't know how-- how long we're going to travel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we all just ate a little bit and tried to hide the other one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And at one point-- and we were so many of us on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no place to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You couldn't turn, even.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was this neighbor of ours with a little boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she was feeding him, and after a while, she also took the rest of the bread.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was trying to hide it from him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he-- and he was crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He wanted more bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was trying to explain to them that he needs it for later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at this point, my father took his bread, and he just took a chunk of it, and he gave it to him.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came to Auschwitz, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were looking through the little windows in the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
